rows.label: qst201613_msg0002
rows.name: Nanakoori, are you okay?

rows.label: qst201613_msg0003
rows.name: ...No. I... I can't do it.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0004
rows.name:
It's understandable to be
nervous at this scale...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0005
rows.name: Take a deep breath and relax your body.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0006
rows.name:
I can't... I'm too scared
to move. I can't speak...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0007
rows.name: This is quite serious...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0008
rows.name: What do we do?!

rows.label: qst201613_msg0009
rows.name:
Should I buy something again, mo?
What do you want to eat, mo?!

rows.label: qst201613_msg0010
rows.name:
...I don't want anything. I
don't think I can swallow... I
don't want to eat anything...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0011
rows.name:
Nanakoori... So many fans are
waiting. What will you do?

rows.label: qst201613_msg0012
rows.name: I... I know, but...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0013
rows.name:
I want to succeed and put an end to
this, I do feel that way, but...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0014
rows.name:
But I wonder why I have to sing
while feeling this scared...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0015
rows.name: Mooo, it's all over, mo!

rows.label: qst201613_msg0016
rows.name:
What should we do? I don't
want to force her, but...

rows.label: qst201613_msg0017
rows.name: Nanakoori is scared of singing, right?

rows.label: qst201613_msg0018
rows.name:
She must be under a lot of
pressure to sing well in front
of a huge crowd and succeed, mo.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0019
rows.name:
But... I think Nanakoori
looked very happy when she
sang for the first time.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0020
rows.name: Singing was supposed to be fun for her.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0021
rows.name:
Indeed. I was struck by her
beautiful singing voice and
happy expression, mo.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0022
rows.name:
How about we ask that girl
from Torigo to come?

rows.label: qst201613_msg0023
rows.name:
I see. You want to remind
her of where she started.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0024
rows.name:
Yes. Then Nanakoori might
be able to sing again.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0025
rows.name:
It seems worth a try, mo.
Everyone, could you bring
that girl here, mo?

rows.label: qst201613_msg0026
rows.name: Of course!

rows.label: qst201613_msg0027
rows.name:
We met her at night at Tretl
Windmill Plaza, right?

rows.label: qst201613_msg0028
rows.name: Yes, that's right.

rows.label: qst201613_msg0029
rows.name: Then let's hurry, mo!
